{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8695813860","title":"周恩来、毛泽东在李广桥支部关于“徐向前最近表现情况”报告上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4544f45377","index":0,"year":1968,"month":12,"day":29,"articleId":"8695813860"},{"id":"81668f1590","index":1,"year":1969,"month":1,"day":3,"articleId":"8695813860"}],"tags":[{"id":"0a84ea94c2","name":"二月逆流","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"0ed2104fe1","name":"徐向前","type":"人物"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"ff92c783-256c-487a-abd2-8e59e9be6390","name":"文革期间毛泽东及中央领导讲话（补篇）（港中文藏书）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"香港中文大学藏书","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/ff92c783-256c-487a-abd2-8e59e9be6390.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"},{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"}]},"publication_details":{"ff92c783-256c-487a-abd2-8e59e9be6390":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7d855c0fee","type":"paragraph","text":"我主要是达么儿点，就是一个讲清理滑级队伍。清题纸队位，选您罚壹，注意一个“准”字。对于一些老同志感，要一二保亚有三看来，是不是牙？所调保者，就是都马他们恋：看符，是看他们以后的情况吃，数不收。我岭惠见，改了也可账，不数也可以，强遇入东改，我配不那么劳成。你言这么几征有要系啦爱，我附才不是请了吗，地球照特技。这个聚不要拉播水发了。周恩来、毛泽东在李广桥支部关于“徐向前最近表现情况”报告上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"ff92c783-256c-487a-abd2-8e59e9be6390","articleId":"8695813860"},{"id":"74983dfb38","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六八半十二月二十九日、","index":1,"publicationId":"ff92c783-256c-487a-abd2-8e59e9be6390","articleId":"8695813860"},{"id":"1f2b0ab99d","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六九一月三日）建议军要办事越柔人找春广桥支部同志误谈，不要情降过干紧察，防止意外。周恩来","index":2,"publicationId":"ff92c783-256c-487a-abd2-8e59e9be6390","articleId":"8695813860"},{"id":"a8ad3f1b54","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月二十九日质有与二月逆流有关的念同态及其家属，额不要然判，是配关系好。","index":3,"publicationId":"ff92c783-256c-487a-abd2-8e59e9be6390","articleId":"8695813860"},{"id":"40569f8da3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽车","index":4,"publicationId":"ff92c783-256c-487a-abd2-8e59e9be6390","articleId":"8695813860"},{"id":"9a8ee05b84","type":"paragraph","text":"一月三日温：北件及中”有理导如题码。","index":5,"publicationId":"ff92c783-256c-487a-abd2-8e59e9be6390","articleId":"8695813860"}],"page":{"id":"926687fd7b","publicationId":"ff92c783-256c-487a-abd2-8e59e9be6390","articleId":"8695813860","start":28,"end":28}}}},"__N_SSG":true}